{"tid":476529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃偉綸：目前東江水「貴及多餘都照買」的收費方式有一定好處","createTime":"2017-11-22T05:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T05:45:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6c43e0b9fc12be9a4fef3e980f1ec4d33a2766cc","tid":476529,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1366208_1_L_20171122123553.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1366208_1_L_20171122123553.jpg&h=7bfc9c74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n粵港雙方達成新東江水供水協議，繼續沿用「統包總額」收費方式買東江水。發展局局長黃偉綸解釋，目前收費做法有一定好處，外界提出的「按量收費」方式未必更好，但未來會繼續和粵方商議不同收費方式。"}]}